# ============================================================================
# Vaporform Environment Configuration
# ============================================================================
#
# IMPORTANT: This file is deprecated in favor of Encore's secret management.
#
# All secrets should now be configured using Encore's built-in secrets manager:
#   - Local development: encore secret set --type local SecretName
#   - Production: encore secret set --type prod SecretName
#   - Development: encore secret set --type dev SecretName
#
# See documentation:
#   - Setup script: ./scripts/setup-local-secrets.sh
#   - Migration guide: ENCORE_SECRETS_MIGRATION.md
#   - Project docs: CLAUDE.md
#
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# Required Encore Secrets
# ============================================================================

# Clerk Authentication (Required)
# - encore secret set --type local ClerkSecretKey
# - encore secret set --type local ClerkPublishableKey
# - encore secret set --type local ClerkWebhookSecret

# AI Services (Required)
# - encore secret set --type local AnthropicAPIKey       # Claude API for code generation
# - encore secret set --type local OpenAIAPIKey          # OpenAI for embeddings only

# MongoDB GridFS (Required)
# - encore secret set --type local MongoDBURI
# Example: mongodb://vaporform:password@localhost:27017/vaporform?authSource=admin

# Qdrant Vector Database (Required)
# - encore secret set --type local QdrantURL
# Example: http://localhost:6333

# User Secret Encryption (Required)
# - encore secret set --type local UserSecretEncryptionKey
# Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
# CRITICAL: Never change this key after data is encrypted!

# ============================================================================
# Optional Encore Secrets
# ============================================================================

# Qdrant API Key (Optional - only if authentication enabled)
# - encore secret set --type local QdrantAPIKey

# Daytona Workspace Management (Optional - workspace features)
# - encore secret set --type local DaytonaAPIKey
# - encore secret set --type local DaytonaAPIURL

# Base Domain (Optional - defaults to vaporform.dev)
# - encore secret set --type local BaseDomain

# ============================================================================
# Quick Setup
# ============================================================================

# Run the interactive setup script:
# ./scripts/setup-local-secrets.sh

